{"tid":1105878,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實意粉 通粉 肥唔肥？","createTime":"2019-04-14T08:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T08:44:38.000Z","uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc30a59e2fba10f52996ba7c065c69698da0ab3","tid":1105878,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個汁就咁用 蕃茄壓蘭佢"},{"pid":"b3b06c664e02984dedcce24e0df5a52b12fa72f5","tid":1105878,"uid":210314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"意粉屬低GI值碳水<br />\n可以食 但不能太多<br />\n致肥有好大部份都係個汁"},{"pid":"3f71b7d1345b975892faefff85814f0d68d70dcc","tid":1105878,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"意粉有好高碳水化合物，有一派覺得carbohydrates, 尤其係麵粉/精米/白糖哩啲 refined carbohydrates會大幅影響血糖，造成美國人既癡肥同糖尿問題。<br />\n另一方面日本飲食都高碳水，不過佢地飲食中都有鹽(sodium)同蔬菜(其中有potassium)可以平衡翻。<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得適量既情況下，我地身體係需要均衡攝取多種營養元素。咁你係食意粉果餐食少d其他糖分就OK。"}]}